p: \rDo you have a favourite Pokemon? Mine is Eevee!
\rI spent so many wonderful years with my little one.
\rEventually, I figured out how to teach Eevee moves outside of its movepool!
\rIf you'd like, I could do the same for you.
\rHowever... Eevee can't evolve while it knows one of these moves. So choose wisely!
\rOh, a shame. Maybe another time, then.

\rYou know, you should really consider getting one!
\rI've been taking care of the plants in Gaea Town.
\rIt is each generation's responsibility to prepare the world for its successors.
\rThat's something I believe with all my heart!
\bGaea Town used to be the home of the First Augur before he disappeared.
\bHe even used to be the Gym Leader here.
\bIt's such a shame he went away. I quite liked the fellow.
\rI heard they're rebuilding the Battle Frontier off of Roggan Town.
\rYou have to sneak your way in, though... you could probably find a way if you knew Rock Climb!
\bHey, kid. Trying to dig your way out of a tough situation?
\bI can help. Let me teach your Pokemon Dig!
\bBwah! I'm glad I could help you.
\bLet me know if I can Dig you out of any more problems in the future!
\bWh... what? How could you refuse! I'm hurt!
\bWh... what? How could you possibly say such a thing? I'm hurt!
\rHey, I'm a Move Tutor for a very specific move.
\rIf you'd like, I could teach a Pokemon Headbutt for you.
\rAnnndddd... there you go! Hopefully that move serves you well!
\rI see. Well, I'm glad you seem all right without my help, then.
\rI see. Well, I'm glad you seem all right without my help, then.
\bI heard they're resetting the Pokemon League with a new Champion soon.
\bI wonder who it's going to be? I heard they came from another region.
\rWelcome to Gaea Town- the most peaceful town in the region.
\rSurprisingly, a lot happens here, but we don't have a lot of visitors because of how cordoned off it is.
\rThat's why the First Augur chose it as a spot to set up his base! Easily defensible!
\bI got to see the entire Jaern broadcast live on TV.
\bYou know, the one where he was outed as a Sky Cultist?
\bIsn't that crazy? What a time we live in where a scandal like that can be exposed and people can watch it that easily!
\bGaea Town is renowned for a couple of things.
\bObviously, the HQ of the First Augur! Who could forget?
\bBut we also have the region's only Dream Guru, and the only merchant from whom you can purchase Plates!
\bAnd of course- we have one of the only two Eevee tutors in the region.
\bAnd so much more! We get so many special guests.
\bNow that you've gotten all 8 badges- all the Pokemon in your Friend Safari should appear for you!
\bIsn't that fantastic? There's so many great things to find there!
\bI heard that Diana was interested in working with Professor Sylvan.
\bI think that's a fantastic idea- I heard she's really good at that kind of thing.
\bI hope I can challenge her in her Gym before she leaves, though!
\bThere's a trainer from a far away region who's expressed interest in being the new Champion over here.
\bBut I guess the current champion has to leave willingly. Somebody's gotta convince him to do that!
\bI'll trade you my Darumaka for any Water-type!
\bWell, come back if you change your mind!

\bWell, come back if you change your mind!
\rHey, \pn. It's good to see you again.
\rListen... it's been one heck of a ride, huh?
\rI heard you beat the Elite Four- for the second time! That's amazing.
\rI don't want to be confined to this region. I'm not happy here.
\rI want to go challenge leagues. I want to go join Contests.
\rI want to go to Hoenn, Sinnoh, Unova, Kalos and even Alola!
\rTorren doesn't have a lot of great memories for me.
\rThat's why I'll be starting over. From scratch.
\rA new team, a new goal, a new purpose.
\rI was going to release all my Pokemon before I left, but...
\rWell, I don't think I should release all of them.
\rI don't know how well Celebi would do in the wild.
\rCelebi and I are destined to be together, after all! I don't think Celebi would be happy to be caught and used by anyone.
\rThat's why, if you'll permit it, I'd like Celebi to travel with you, \pn.
\rWill you do it? Will you let Celebi join you on your adventure?
\rAnd now it's time for me to be off, I guess.
\rHopefully I'll see you again. If you ever decide to leave Torren, let me know! I'll be glad to show you around wherever the winding road leads me.
